text: Eben Vorster (born 23 April 1997) is a South African swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre freestyle event at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Male butterfly swimmers Category:Male freestyle swimmers Category:People from Bellville, Western Cape Category:South African male swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Commonwealth Games
